    "This is especially beneficial for non-native English-speaking researchers, enabling proficient writing and reducing linguistic bias in academic publishing [28,29].",
    "By improving the linguistic quality of academic papers, LLMs may serve as valuable supplementary tools that improve the overall clarity and accessibility of scholarly communication.",
